se=E2=80=99s arguments or=C2=A0cowed by Coinbase=E2=80=99s promises to figh=
t the case to the bitter end or chastened by congressional hearings critici=
zing its regulatory approach. The filing of the lawsuit collapsed the uncer=
tainty; the SEC is actually doing the thing it was expected to do. So the s=
tock went down.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So I suppose you could have woken up on Monday=
 and thought =E2=80=9Cwell, I know the SEC is probably going to sue Coinbas=
